SUMMARY:Harmony and Power | A Screening of the Documentary "Resonancia"
DESCRIPTION:Students\, sign up here &gt\;  What begins as a search for me
 lody evolves into a profound journey of artistic and personal discovery\,
  culminating in a public concert where visual art and music merge in a po
 werful expression of creativity and courage. The screening will be presen
 ted and discussed by producer Cathy BarbashŌĆöformer Orchestra Manager of
  The Philadelphia Orchestra and now an independent international producer
  and cultural diplomacy specialistŌĆöoffering insight into the film's cul
 tural and artistic impact.Harmony and Power: A Summit on Cultural Diploma
 cyPresented by the Hamilton Lugar School and Jacobs School of Music  With
  panel discussions\, presentations\, workshops\, and concerts\, Harmony a
 nd Power will explore how cultural diplomacy shapes power and global conn
 ections. Participants include renowned scholars\, practitioners\, perform
 ers\, and students from a variety of disciplines.
X-ALT-DESC;FMTTYPE=text/html:<p><a class="Hyperlink SCXW100065811 BCX0" h
 ref="https://app.joinhandshake.com/events/1913204/share_preview" target="
 _blank" rel="noreferrer noopener"><span class="TextRun Underlined SCXW100
 065811 BCX0" lang="EN-US" xml:lang="EN-US" data-contrast="none"><span cla
 ss="NormalTextRun SCXW100065811 BCX0" data-ccp-charstyle="Hyperlink">Stud
 ents\, sign up here &gt\;</span></span></a><span class="EOP SCXW100065811
  BCX0" data-ccp-props="{&quot\;201341983&quot\;:0\,&quot\;335559739&quot\
 ;:0\,&quot\;335559740&quot\;:240}"></span></p><p>  What begins as a searc
 h for melody evolves into a profound journey of artistic and personal dis
 covery\, culminating in a public concert where visual art and music merge
  in a powerful expression of creativity and courage. The screening will b
 e presented and discussed by producer Cathy BarbashŌĆöformer Orchestra Ma
 nager of The Philadelphia Orchestra and now an independent international 
 producer and cultural diplomacy specialistŌĆöoffering insight into the fi
 lm's cultural and artistic impact.<br /><br /><strong>Harmony and Power: 
 A Summit on Cultural Diplomacy</strong><br /><br /><em>Presented by the H
 amilton Lugar School and Jacobs School of Music<br /></em><br />  With pa
 nel discussions\, presentations\, workshops\, and concerts\, Harmony and 
 Power will explore how cultural diplomacy shapes power and global connect
 ions. Participants include renowned scholars\, practitioners\, performers
 \, and students from a variety of disciplines.</p>
